<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset Styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* Hero Section Styling */
    .hero-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background-color: #f8d0c1;
      background-image: url('images/home1.jpg'); /* Optional: Update with your image */
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .hero-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero-section .shop-now-btn {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: rgb(244, 96, 96);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .hero-section .shop-now-btn:hover {
      background-color: rgb(244, 96, 96);
    }

    /* Feature Section */
    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px;
      width: 200px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-item i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #ff8c00;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature-item p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Flower Section */
    .flower-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .flower-card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 15px;
      max-width: 300px;
      background-color: white;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .flower-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .flower-card img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 250px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .flower-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .flower-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    /* Special Offer Section */
    .special-offer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background-color: rgb(244, 96, 96);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .special-offer img {
      width: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }

    .special-offer h2, .special-offer h1 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .special-offer .shop-btn {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: white;
      color: rgb(244, 96, 96);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .special-offer .shop-btn:hover {
      background-color: #ffcc80;
    }

    /* Testimonials Section */
    .testimonials {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonial {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .testimonial div {
      width: 250px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonial img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* CTA Section */
    .cta-container {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-container img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-container h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cta-container p {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-container a {
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: rgb(244, 96, 96);
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .cta-container a:hover {
      background-color: #e67e00;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .hero-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .feature-item {
        width: 150px;
      }

      .flower-card {
        max-width: 250px;
      }

      .special-offer img {
        width: 300px;
        margin-right: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .cta-container {
        padding: 30px 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1 style="color: white;">WELCOME TO FLORALFLAIR</h1>
      <h2 style="color: white;">Letâ€™s Make Beautiful Flowers a Part of Your Life</h2>
      <a href="/flowers"><button class="shop-now-btn"><b>SHOP NOW</b></button></a>
    </div>
  </header>



  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-item">
      <i class="bi bi-phone-vibrate"></i>
      <p>Order Online</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <i class="bi bi-truck"></i>
      <p>Free Shipping</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <i class="bi bi-percent"></i>
      <p>Big Discounts</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <i class="bi bi-wallet2"></i>
      <p>Safe Payment</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Flowers Section -->
  <section id="flowers">
    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Featured Flowers</h2>
    {{#if flowers.length}}
    <div class="flower-container">
      {{#each flowers}}
        <div class="flower-card">
          <img src="/{{this.image}}" alt="{{this.name}}">
          <h2>{{this.name}}</h2>
          <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{this.description}}</p>
          <p><strong>Price:</strong> ${{this.price}}</p>
        </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{else}}
      <p>No flowers available at the moment.</p>
    {{/if}}
  </section>

  <!-- Special Offer Section -->
  <section class="special-offer">
    <div>
      <h2>SPECIAL OFFER</h2>
      <h1>Your Floral Journey Begins Here: Get 20% Off Your First Order!</h1>
      <a href="/flowers" class="shop-btn">Shop Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials Section -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <h2>TESTIMONIAL</h2>
    <h1>Hear From Our Happy Customers !!</h1><br>
    <div class="testimonial">
      <div>
        <p><b>I've been a loyal customer of FloralFlair for years, and they never cease to amaze me. The flowers are always fresh, the arrangements are stunning, and the service is top-notch.</b></p>
        <img src="images/home3.jpg" alt="Riya Kapoor">
        <h4>Riya Kapoor</h4>
        <span>Wedding Planner</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p><b>I've always admired FloralFlair for the quality they provide, and they always find ways to amaze me. The flowers, arrangements, the service... all are always out of this world.</b></p>
        <img src="images/home4.jpg" alt="Nishika Garg">
        <h4>Nishika Garg</h4>
        <span>Designer</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p><b>I recently used FloralFlair for my daughter's wedding, and I couldn't have been happier with the results. The wedding florals were breathtaking, and the team went above and beyond to bring perfection.</b></p>
        <img src="images/home5.jpg" alt="Ved Kundra">
        <h4>Ved Kundra</h4>
        <span>Business Owner</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <div class="cta-container">
    <img src="images/home2.jpg" alt="Floral Shop">
    <h3>CALL TO ACTION</h3>
    <p>Explore Our Exquisite Floral Collections & Shop Now for the Perfect Blooms</p>
    <a href="/flowers">Shop Now</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

